Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.03,0:01:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They seem strange and alien.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.71,0:01:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Primitive and peculiar,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.85,0:01:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,they are unlike any flora or fauna known to us.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.83,0:01:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,From time immemorial,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.33,0:01:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,men have feared these misshapen entities,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.13,0:01:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,which came to be known as "mushi."
