Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.63,0:02:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandfather...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.67,0:02:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,where are we going?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.71,0:02:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're traveling to the place that will be your home for the foreseeable future.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.93,0:02:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Until you can finally see them, \Nyou must not set foot outside of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.67,0:02:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I clear?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.93,0:02:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you must resent something, resent your blood.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.35,0:02:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse the dark.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.89,0:02:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And hate the mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:08.04,Mushisode Title,,0,0,0,eptitle,{\fad(2000,0)\an7\bord0\blur0.6\p1\c&H999477&\pos(-2,68)\fscx600\fscy90}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100
Dialogue: 2,0:03:02.03,0:03:08.04,Mushisode Title,,0,0,0,eptitle,{\an4\fad(2000,0)\blur0.6\pos(180,110)}Path of Overgrowth
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.43,0:04:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, here it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.15,0:04:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. That what you need?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.69,0:04:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. This is it.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.98,0:04:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You always have the good stuff.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.50,0:04:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.45,0:04:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,One more thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.69,0:04:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I also came here to ask about something.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.23,0:04:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Rumor has it that mushi have been \Nbehaving erratically on the nearby mountain.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.49,0:04:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you tell me more about that?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.49,0:04:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The head of the main family's already investigating it.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.75,0:04:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This here is Minai clan territory.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.56,0:04:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best if outsider mushi-shi just stay out of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.47,0:04:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.67,0:04:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I was given this letter, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.84,0:05:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The outlying village?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.13,0:05:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It used to be just down this road.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.62,0:05:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's deserted now.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.55,0:05:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A while back, the land over there became completely barren.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.99,0:06:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A bit strange, don't you think?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.85,0:06:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How the dead flora here has suddenly come back to life, I mean.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.35,0:06:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen anything quite like it.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.85,0:06:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.29,0:06:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We Minai will take care of this matter ourselves.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.88,0:06:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stick your nose where it doesn't belong.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.37,0:06:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be the oldest mushi-shi clan,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.99,0:06:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but that doesn't give you the right to monopolize any matter.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.27,0:07:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That hair...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.21,0:07:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be that Ginko fellow.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.13,0:07:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard about you from Tama, the servant of the Karibusa clan.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.75,0:07:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem particularly attached to mushi.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.13,0:07:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How absurd.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.17,0:07:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Halfhearted mushi-shi aren't welcome here.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.09,0:07:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Begone.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.81,0:07:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't {\i1}you{\i0} the halfhearted ones?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.37,0:07:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.45,0:07:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear your clan is only interested in one type of mushi.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.41,0:07:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps that's what has her concerned.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.25,0:07:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I was asked to oversee this investigation, you see.
