Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:59.08,MushiNext,,0,0,0,,{\an4\blur3\c&H53504E&\fax0.23\fscx67\fscy63\frz298.8\move(565,274,565,66,24,9992)\alpha&HB0&}to assist the head of the Minai clan with his investigation.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.07,0:07:59.08,MushiNext,,0,0,0,,{\an4\blur1.2\c&H53504E&\fax0.23\fscx67\fscy63\frz298.8\move(565,274,565,66,24,9992)}to assist the head of the Minai clan with his investigation.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.67,0:07:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unbelievable how whimsical Tanyuu is sometimes.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.83,0:07:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like she's completely unaware of her situation.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.23,0:08:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be nice being so carefree.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.65,0:08:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I received word that the fourth scribe of the Karibusa clan has been born.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.01,0:08:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.23,0:08:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They are the family we have been serving for centuries.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.29,0:08:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Long ago, during the great cataclysm, \Na strange type of mushi appeared before us.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.79,0:09:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,At a time when all other living beings and mushi were rotting away, this mushi possessed great power.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.53,0:09:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It sought to use that power to kill all other life-forms.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.07,0:09:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We dubbed it "The Forbidden Mushi."
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.99,0:09:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who finally put a stop to it \Nwas our ancestor, a Minai mushi-shi.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.52,0:09:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,However, in order to do so, \Nhe had to seal it in a person.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.42,0:09:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A member of the Karibusa clan consented to becoming the mushi's container.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.87,0:09:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But the mushi continued to be passed down \Nalong the Karibusa bloodline,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.09,0:09:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and to this day, it still binds their bodies.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.47,0:10:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We must find a way to eradicate this mushi as quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.29,0:10:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, it might reemerge the moment another cataclysm strikes.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.31,0:10:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, no one knows its true form anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.27,0:10:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father, and his father before him, \Nspent their entire lives investigating this mushi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.16,0:10:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Kumado, my boy...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.25,0:10:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you must inherit their will.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.59,0:10:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm... unable to see mushi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.63,0:10:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Father called me pathetic because of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.43,0:11:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be able to soon enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.41,0:11:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you remain here, you'll be able to see them... \Nwhether you want to or not.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.15,0:11:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no ordinary place.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.13,0:11:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It is called a "Path of Overgrowth."
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.89,0:11:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It is one of the routes mushi take to burst forth from the earth.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.19,0:11:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is on the border between our world and the mushi's world.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.79,0:11:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You must never stray too far down this path.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.45,0:12:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do, you'll never be the same again.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.77,0:12:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They're really starting to multiply.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.07,0:12:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And many of them, I'm seeing for the first time.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.47,0:12:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.34,0:12:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What is {\i1}that{\i0}?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.01,0:12:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to catch some of these.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.21,0:12:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.63,0:13:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.35,0:13:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.31,0:13:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A Path of Overgrowth.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.83,0:13:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why here? There's not even a River of Light here.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.23,0:13:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.32,0:13:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going inside to check things out.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.35,0:13:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.99,0:13:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting cold feet, are we?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.05,0:13:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No one would {\i1}willingly{\i0} set foot \Nin a Path of Overgrowth.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.35,0:13:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you ask me,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.57,0:13:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,it feels just like home.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.41,0:13:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Is that so?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.07,0:13:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.41,0:13:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,quite unfortunate.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.85,0:14:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How long has it been since I came to live in this place?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.85,0:14:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The darkness...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.64,0:14:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's shaking!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.27,0:15:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I still can't see them, but I feel a presence all around me.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.43,0:15:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel them looking at me all the time!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.19,0:15:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Are those things... mushi?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.80,0:15:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they are not.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.79,0:15:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are manifestations of your fears.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.35,0:15:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They are but mere illusions created by your mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.37,0:15:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You have not yet awakened your five senses.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.13,0:15:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it's only a matter of time now.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.75,0:16:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon, the shackles that bind you shall disappear.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.83,0:16:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Shackles?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.45,0:16:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I put it?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.79,0:16:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it would be most accurate to call those shackles... your soul.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.80,0:16:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But if my soul disappears,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.37,0:16:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,will I even still be alive?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.55,0:16:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.45,0:16:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I will replace it with something else.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.45,0:17:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eventually, I stopped seeing the illusions.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.90,0:17:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I became engulfed by that darkness, all the way down to my dreams.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.31,0:18:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.65,0:18:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.22,0:19:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this... scent?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.19,0:20:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's strangely sweet...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.03,0:20:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and yet also bitter.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.19,0:20:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you come to?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.89,0:20:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you recognize me?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.57,0:20:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.45,0:21:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, feast your eyes upon them at last.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.69,0:21:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what a Path of Overgrowth
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.57,0:21:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and the entire world
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.69,0:21:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,truly look like.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.69,0:21:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Found it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.73,0:21:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If it'd make you feel more comfortable, you can wait here.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.76,0:22:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything he says gets on my nerves.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:13.25,0:22:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I suspect you two won't get along, \Nbut could you please go and help him out?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.55,0:22:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who else to ask.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:25.19,0:22:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Minai mushi-shi sometimes seem \Nlike they're lacking a certain something.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:33.77,0:22:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama won't say a word about it,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:37.53,0:22:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm sure it's because they've gone through immense pain and suffering...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:44.75,0:22:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,all because of the mushi sealed right here.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:51.59,0:22:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a bad feeling this time, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:00.93,0:23:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you please go help him out \Nand make sure he doesn't do anything reckless?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:21.81,0:23:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I've got no other choice.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:42.29,0:23:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Tanyuu?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:45.27,0:23:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the man who is to succeed as the head of the Minai clan.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:50.69,0:23:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Kumado.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:59.81,0:24:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2\i1}Perhaps because she wanted to help us, \Nsince we were similar in age and had no friends,
Dialogue: 10,0:24:05.01,0:24:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tama often invited Kumado to our mansion.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:15.67,0:24:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd you go this time?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:18.37,0:24:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to the west coast.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:20.20,0:24:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you bring me any souvenirs?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:21.89,0:24:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:25.43,0:24:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:28.13,0:24:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all different shapes and sizes!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:31.75,0:24:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:33.15,0:24:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this one?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:36.45,0:24:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know there was an agate in there.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:39.89,0:24:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you want to give me something this pretty?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:44.81,0:24:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:46.87,0:24:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really care either way.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:55.73,0:24:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tama?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:58.96,0:25:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Does Kumado hate me or something?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:03.97,0:25:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen him smile. Not even once.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:09.97,0:25:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to his harsh upbringing, \Nthat boy's soul has grown cold.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:19.17,0:25:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,However, given time,
Dialogue: 10,0:25:22.82,0:25:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm certain that warmth will flow into it again.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:26.99,0:25:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't hold it against him.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:35.33,0:25:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:36.60,0:25:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It must've been really tough \Nto cross that mountain range!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:42.43,0:25:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, I bet the view \Nfrom the summit made it all worth it.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:49.49,0:25:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:51.39,0:25:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just see really far.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:01.05,0:26:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, I've never even seen what lies beyond that hill.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:09.05,0:26:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If I told you I was a little envious of you, \Nwould that make you mad?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:16.51,0:26:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you went to the other side of that hill, \Nyou'd find that there's nothing special there either.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:22.31,0:26:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter where you go, \Nyou'll wind up feeling the same way.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:15.59,0:27:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're up here after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:20.85,0:27:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kumado,{kuma-dono, clearly}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:22.60,0:27:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,you were right.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:28.51,0:27:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter where I run to, everything's the same.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:24.25,0:28:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:37.95,0:28:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:41.93,0:28:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, some time later,
Dialogue: 10,0:28:45.67,0:28:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I came to see Kumado as a completely different person.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:55.03,0:28:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His appearance hadn't changed any,
Dialogue: 10,0:28:58.05,0:29:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I still couldn't help but feel he was a stranger.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:02.89,0:29:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Kumado?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:05.39,0:29:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure it's you, Kumado?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:09.67,0:29:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:12.95,0:29:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, all right.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:51.39,0:29:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This path doesn't seem too old.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:58.33,0:29:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:59.61,0:30:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the exit.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:01.37,0:30:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still open.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:03.73,0:30:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There should have been a River of Light here by now.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:07.25,0:30:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be due to the lack of a mushi lord to conceal the exit.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:10.69,0:30:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this explains the state of that deserted village.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:15.65,0:30:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A Path of Overgrowth, if left open, would blur \Nthe border between mushi and living organisms.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:21.96,0:30:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Within that outlying village, death is no longer definite.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:28.63,0:30:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And if this exit gets any bigger,
Dialogue: 10,0:30:32.97,0:30:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the balance of life is going to come crashing down.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:39.42,0:30:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A cataclysm, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:44.86,0:30:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you planning to do?!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:47.99,0:30:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We have but one job.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:51.45,0:30:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This may be an omen foretelling \Nthe reemergence of the Forbidden Mushi.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:56.21,0:31:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, it's even possible that it has already reappeared at the end of this path.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:01.21,0:31:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, we must go and stop it now.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:06.49,0:31:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Before anything else, we have to close this exit!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:09.14,0:31:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The sooner we cut off the mushi's influence, the better.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:11.40,0:31:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help me out!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:12.73,0:31:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can prevent a cataclysm from occurring, the Forbidden Mushi won't appear.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:16.47,0:31:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So sealing this place off comes first!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:20.75,0:31:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to fulfill my clan's duty, \NI threw away everything...
Dialogue: 10,0:31:27.17,0:31:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,all for some elusive mushi of legend that never appears.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:35.27,0:31:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point, I {\i1}want{\i0} it to show up.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:54.33,0:31:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Something huge is back there.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:00.05,0:32:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! What do you think you'll accomplish by yourself?!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:04.19,0:32:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:08.01,0:32:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He's being so reckless.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:09.43,0:32:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he have a death wish?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:17.53,0:32:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The exit's already gotten bigger.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:41.67,0:32:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The mushi have disappeared.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:46.19,0:32:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:01.77,0:33:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A mushi corpse?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:06.23,0:33:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No...
Dialogue: 10,0:33:07.71,0:33:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's still alive.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:10.65,0:33:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the state that it's in...
Dialogue: 10,0:34:03.89,0:34:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you swarming all over me for?
Dialogue: 10,0:34:10.75,0:34:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Search me all you want.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:13.75,0:34:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never find what you're looking for, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:20.80,0:34:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I already gave it to you a long time ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:30.49,0:34:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:36.64,0:34:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:38.19,0:34:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Or they'll take your soul!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:54.61,0:34:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's so cold.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:58.01,0:35:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It feels like a freezing wind is blowing throughout my body.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:19.69,0:35:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where am I?
Dialogue: 10,0:35:22.53,0:35:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this place?
Dialogue: 10,0:35:29.39,0:35:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that...
Dialogue: 10,0:35:32.79,0:35:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}me?
Dialogue: 10,0:35:45.93,0:35:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The moon again?
Dialogue: 10,0:35:50.93,0:35:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't it set already, though?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:10.23,0:36:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:12.47,0:36:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you follow me?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:06.99,0:37:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally made it out of the woods.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:25.19,0:37:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, this is...
Dialogue: 10,0:37:42.15,0:37:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that... Tanyuu?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:48.13,0:37:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it's the Tanyuu from long before I met her.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:58.39,0:37:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:33.39,0:38:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:42.75,0:38:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,His soul is missing.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:56.67,0:39:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Did that thing... save me?
Dialogue: 10,0:39:04.73,0:39:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What {\i1}was{\i0} that just now?
Dialogue: 10,0:39:29.11,0:39:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work, Ginko.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:33.85,0:39:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll pay you later, so would you mind leaving for now?
Dialogue: 10,0:39:41.49,0:39:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the Minai mushi-shi have gotten involved with something crazy.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:47.87,0:39:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing was an artificial mushi made from kouki.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:56.35,0:40:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You use it as the substitute for someone's soul \Nand then make them go after mushi.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:00.67,0:40:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it ever gets out, \Nyou replace it with another.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:05.25,0:40:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really making your family repeat such a process?
Dialogue: 10,0:40:11.95,0:40:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't,
Dialogue: 10,0:40:14.77,0:40:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,there is a path we won't be able to progress down.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:35.79,0:40:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Beings that shuffle along this mortal coil even after having lost their souls...
Dialogue: 10,0:40:49.27,0:40:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What could they be?
Dialogue: 10,0:41:05.37,0:41:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who could they be?
Dialogue: 10,0:41:37.61,0:41:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe you my thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:39.97,0:41:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If it weren't for you, I would've lost my soul too.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:46.09,0:41:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I just hate those Sanekuimushi, is all.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:52.93,0:41:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 10,0:42:00.81,0:42:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for making you wait.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:26.03,0:42:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So then, you finally closed the exit to that Path of Overgrowth?
Dialogue: 10,0:42:31.79,0:42:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,More or less. I made some temporary repairs.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:36.29,0:42:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}It was a sort of emergency exit that the mushi created \Nin order to escape the massive outbreak of Sanekuimushi.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:43.37,0:42:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Providing that the Sanekuimushi go back to normal, the exit will be sealed in time.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:48.39,0:42:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanekuimushi, or "Core-Eating" mushi...
Dialogue: 10,0:42:51.77,0:42:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They're mushi that reside in a \NPath of Overgrowth and devour souls, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:42:58.21,0:43:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you think of any reasons \Nbehind their massive outbreak?
Dialogue: 10,0:43:03.39,0:43:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet, no.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:07.55,0:43:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I can only guess that it's another of the mushi abnormalities \Nthat have occurred within the last twenty years.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:15.61,0:43:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you believe it to be a bad omen?
Dialogue: 10,0:43:19.99,0:43:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say for sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:23.45,0:43:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, I still couldn't find out anything about the Forbidden Mushi.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:31.94,0:43:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You needn't rush, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:35.45,0:43:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm quite prepared to spend \Nthe rest of my life with this mushi.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:46.11,0:43:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kumado...
Dialogue: 10,0:43:49.27,0:43:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if nothing ever changes,
Dialogue: 10,0:43:55.23,0:43:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,we are not alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:01.75,0:44:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Not in the least.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:23.19,0:44:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it taste good?
Dialogue: 10,0:44:26.39,0:44:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:29.03,0:44:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it does!
Dialogue: 10,0:44:30.96,0:44:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, you can have some too.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:32.48,0:44:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:34.53,0:44:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what "delicious" tastes like.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:36.32,0:44:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you're being pretty forceful.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:39.20,0:44:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet, you.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:41.41,0:44:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, are you sure this is "delicious"?
Dialogue: 10,0:44:44.73,0:44:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You really don't have a taste for the finer things, do you?
Dialogue: 10,0:44:47.77,0:44:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty rude of you.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:49.97,0:44:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a matter of personal preference.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:53.74,0:44:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
